      <title>美国清算机构 DTCC 称处理问题已得到解决，行业已实现 T+1 目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/dtcc-says-processing-issue-resolved-as-industry-hits-t-1-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管隔夜结算系统有所延迟，但金融行业在新的一日结算规则实施的第一天就实现了更快处理美国证券交易的关键目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/dtcc-says-processing-issue-resolved-as-industry-hits-t-1-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 18:33:45 GMT</pubDate>
