      <title>埃克森美孚誓言成为股东民主的“有力倡导者”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/exxon-shareholders-vote-with-board-on-all-proxy-proposals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃克森美孚公司承诺成为股东权利的“有力倡导者”，因为它正与激进投资者对峙，这家石油巨头指责激进投资者滥用美国代理投票制度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/exxon-shareholders-vote-with-board-on-all-proxy-proposals</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 15:38:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
