      <title>耶鲁大学任命石溪大学校长领导常春藤联盟应对美国动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/yale-turns-to-stony-brook-s-president-to-lead-ivy-during-tumult</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国高等教育因学生抗议、教师多元化和招生等问题陷入动荡之际，耶鲁大学任命长岛石溪大学校长莫里·麦金尼斯 (Maurie McInnis) 为新校长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/yale-turns-to-stony-brook-s-president-to-lead-ivy-during-tumult</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:00:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BMO 股价下跌，因银行暗示信贷困境将持续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/bmo-earnings-miss-estimates-on-higher-than-expected-provisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蒙特利尔银行公布的盈利不及分析师预期，因拨备的潜在信贷损失金额超出预期，该行股价出现四年来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/bmo-earnings-miss-estimates-on-higher-than-expected-provisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 10:15:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市下跌，因美国国债销售疲软推高美国收益率：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券市场的下滑拖累了股市，因为美国国债销量再次疲软，引发了人们对供应增加的担忧，这可能会继续推高收益率，而美联储并不急于降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 22:19:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
